.page-title.bordered
  %h2 Flash messages

%p This flash messages system has three different modes: Form, Fullscreen and Async.
%ul
  %li <code>.flash-form</code> messages&mdash;typically used in/near forms.
  %li <code>.flash-fullscreen</code> messages&mdash;used generally when the action is not "form-based" (successfully reordering contacts; selecting a featured show) or when the user is deleting a record.
  %li <code>.flash-async</code> messages&mdash;used when providing notifications outside of the typical request/response cycle.

%p.double-margin-bottom
  Each mode has two versions <code>.flash-notice</code> and <code>.flash-error</code>.

